# 🧱 ERD (Entity Relationship Design)

### Core Entities

- Customer
- Address
- Order
- OrderItem
- Product
- Payment

### Relationships

- Customer → Orders (1 to Many)
- Customer → Address (1 to Many)
- Order → OrderItems (1 to Many)
- Order → Payment (1 to 1)
- Product → OrderItems (1 to Many)

